caption:
Manchester United have now conceded 18 goals in all competitions in December, their most in a single month since March 1964 (also 18). 

Isak's goal was also the 7th time they have conceded inside the opening five minutes of a Premier League game at Old Trafford since the beginning of 2023. 

It only happened seven times between 2013 & 2022. 🤯
